Flask API Example Skeleton

Build API endpoints:

    1) Providers with data:
        - Name
        - Email
        - Phone Number
        - Language
        - Currency

    2) Service areas of business operation for the providers:
        - name of the area
        - related provider
        - price in this area (to compare with the other prices)
        - polygon of the area

    3) Prices query endpoint:
        - by given latitude, longitude
        - return all polygons, containing this point

Deploy the code to Docker.
